vailability-information-18191\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Platform Availability Matrix</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"byb1665702735623__note_w265ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3b3b3_w266ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3b3_w267ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3_w268ab1b5b1b1b3b7_w269ab1b5b1b1b3_w270ab1b5b1b1_w271ab1b5b1_w272ab1b5_w273ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Transaction Manager (TM) support is not available in the current Uniface release.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byb1665702735623__table_d4691e1_d4692e1_d4693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported utilities</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byb1665702735623__table_d4691e1_d4692e1_d4693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Create Table is supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byb1665702735623__table_d4691e1_d4692e1_d4693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">SQL support</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byb1665702735623__table_d4691e1_d4692e1_d4693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byb1665702735623__table_d4691e1_d4692e1_d4693e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Stored procedures support</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byb1665702735623__table_d4691e1_d4692e1_d4693e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzu1665702542108.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DBMS Connector Overview</a><p>This se