e Platform Availability Matrix . Note: Transaction Manager (TM) support is not available in the current Uniface release. Supported utilities Create Table is supported. SQL support Supported. Stored procedures support Supported. Related Links DBMS Connector Overview This section provides an overview of supported functionality and limitations for all DBMS connectors. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}